Package com.amplitude.skylab

Class SkylabUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplitude.skylab.SkylabUser
  • public class SkylabUser
extends java.lang.Object
    The Skylab user context object. This is an immutable object that can be created using a SkylabUser.Builder. Example usage: SkylabUser.builder().setLanguage("en").build()
